Chopped Canada - Season 1, Episode 20




The Spruce is Loose

One chef finds himself in hot water when mussels and mushrooms appear in the appetizer round. A beverage from the space age makes for a sweet surprise in the dinner round. The chefs spruce things up in the dessert round with a sweet basket straight from the tropics.




Original Air Date: 15-May-2014
